{"id":"2c45df69ef9aeb6e2e2018f28b8dd00d5c392948bf4b342bc58e040ce9ac69a9","item_id":"0e0880bf07:0","text":"Depth of Field (DOF)（景深）是一种摄影技术，用于在构图中表达 scale（尺度/大小）和关注区域。"}
{"id":"ba1445add455512a98878b97e03f3ad9710ec8bed79405f0bb7c9d82bfccd55d","item_id":"0e0880bf07:1","text":"巧妙使用它，可以把 viewer（观看者）的注意力引导到图像中的特定部分，并通过正确模拟真实世界 lens（镜头）来提升 photorealism（照片级真实感）。"}
{"id":"7f1438f05cb8d9e2066d4c723539ff395e12b247df740e9ef3af7bcabe83bdf9","item_id":"0e0880bf07:2","text":"RenderMan 提供 depth of field（景深）控制，可生成真实且有表现力的图像。也有一些 non-physical（非物理）的选项，非常适合创建 art-directed imagery（艺术指导图像）。"}
{"id":"ce830230603a7151032a9e1160797777027a926352ceeb22edef00bbc76c312f","item_id":"0e0880bf07:3","text":"depth of field（景深）的 render cost（渲染成本）可能较高，因为它会产生 noise（噪点），需要更多 samples（采样）才能 converge（收敛）。但效果可能很出色。"}
{"id":"fd7f1ff50c2d0ff450e080a3b5a23983e9e061e1f6b866f42195da65d21ac6b2","item_id":"0e0880bf07:4","text":"要在 Blender 中开始使用 DOF，请前往要渲染 DOF 的 camera（摄像机）的 camera data properties（摄像机数据属性）"}
{"id":"1f272e023a751f879e7e96f9ef3e14ece424e3b91bf11b002de315a71d761b86","item_id":"0e0880bf07:5","text":"，并点击 Depth of Field 旁边的复选框，如下所示。"}
{"id":"9ccf75d0c4134a523eb5185eaa9c74f1240ef87be212f7cf09ccbdd14bf8dc9b","item_id":"0e0880bf07:6","text":"F Stop:（F 值：）"}
{"id":"9f6c62f0083dee9404e5aab15afee33228a928e24502e6bdedb0f2ea32dcf5c5","item_id":"0e0880bf07:7","text":"与真实 camera lens（摄像机镜头）一样，此设置控制该效果的强度。较低数值会增加 blur（模糊），较高数值会减少 blur（模糊）。"}
{"id":"931fbc79d847107c55cbab79030ef4cb9a06a774ec4d86874505cbfc43e591a1","item_id":"0e0880bf07:8","text":"Ratio:（比例：）Depth of field（景深）宽高比。"}
{"id":"9d0a3f67dd03d45479a166f9d2e0b44245b9afa520c49631ab6be4c1e7bc2e99","item_id":"0e0880bf07:9","text":"Blades:（叶片数：）"}
{"id":"078bf2b864ecc8780730ef452f3835838cf4284d3a2dac1bf854d454428fda28","item_id":"0e0880bf07:10","text":"这决定 bokeh（焦外成像）效果的形状。如果选择少于三条边（triangle，三角形），bokeh 会是圆形。"}
{"id":"3e18a50849b7f25c46d5e0145c0278947beb51a460ef4f6700d1544031ddf859","item_id":"0e0880bf07:11","text":"Rotation:（旋转：）"}
{"id":"5e37a182b1ef1353ba45a28199d2059ab8bf72bb22bb02e25f8d25f20cee9a8b","item_id":"0e0880bf07:12","text":"这控制非圆形 bokeh 形状中边相交处的角度（Number of Sides 大于 2）。"}
{"id":"6d2a81f0afeb6766bb151972b2c37e7deb5627ecfc333dfc919c1481aadf767f","item_id":"0e0880bf07:13","text":"Roundness:（圆润度：）"}
{"id":"08e2ee05a4f04531c0d8652c6c2ffd11cd5b6cff354cea8a7a139e2da8f6f59c","item_id":"0e0880bf07:14","text":"0 到 1 的值会使形状向外弯曲或扩展，让它更圆润。0 到 -1 的值会向内弯曲，形成更尖锐的点。"}
{"id":"f18f26870f635d476cf6b69f4cbc948e1692b6e05b9287e0284770182271cabd","item_id":"0e0880bf07:15","text":"Density:（密度：）"}
{"id":"48d97d8244290e7ecdc1e8985ce277efce5d37b1ae00dce56a6d0060c21ab8a1","item_id":"0e0880bf07:16","text":"这控制整个 bokeh 形状上的亮度。0 到 1 会让外边缘更亮，类似 catadioptric lens（反射折射镜头）（可以查一下，很有意思）。0 到 -1 会让中心更亮，并向边缘 falloff（衰减）。"}
{"id":"507eb1c021dda12ed35db00137541e69c82f60f87a3058d4e67add421082fbd6","item_id":"0e0880bf07:17","text":"有关各种 aperture（光圈）控制的更多信息，请参见"}
{"id":"6b70f7a055f981034e0ed0a4628653e652794a1474c1488e605b3b783964c229","item_id":"0e0880bf07:18","text":"Bokeh"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"0e0880bf07:19","text":"。"}
{"id":"9d3cab2b5efed4eaef42a707dbc813da2ffad53220aa713b5f3c950596fe35f5","item_id":"0e0880bf07:20","text":"Focus（对焦）"}
{"id":"5635fd14700601915bb75301077c8eba8154a6c1adedcc5f1b2da54bd33b023c","item_id":"0e0880bf07:21","text":"Distance:（距离：）"}
{"id":"2c4bcdb9e447272558462cc7b4af867ab1e8cdc0f06f0a444528ab8d0feb2d63","item_id":"0e0880bf07:22","text":"到你希望 in-focus（焦内/清晰）的对象或位置的距离，以 scene grid units（场景网格单位）度量。这称为"}
{"id":"f3e7e4ed62368a7553dc3593d2a6679077649dbb97f5033a76567db22e0332b4","item_id":"0e0880bf07:23","text":"Focal Plane（对焦平面）"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"0e0880bf07:24","text":"。"}
{"id":"755f58ad2eac33947678804da1f6a3999de65409c5eb6fd0bcbfef18e4cce0ad","item_id":"0e0880bf07:25","text":"Focus Object:（对焦对象：）你也可以从场景中选择一个对象作为距离。RfB 会优先使用此值，而不是 Distance 中设置的值。"}
